com.rscja.custom

Class M775Authenticate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.deviceapi.UhfBase
      • com.rscja.deviceapi.RFIDWithUHFUART
        • com.rscja.custom.M775Authenticate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IM775Authenticate, IHandheldRFID, ISingleAntenna, IUHF, IUHFOfAndroidUart

    public class M775Authenticate
extends RFIDWithUHFUART
implements IM775Authenticate
    英频杰特殊标签定制
    Special label customization
    第一步:通过RFIDWithUHFUART.init(Context context) 连接读写器。
    Step 1: Connect to the usb of the reader viaRFIDWithUHFUART.init(Context context)

    第二步： 如果是设置参数，连接成功之后，调用对应的函数设置参数、读写操作。 盘点标签之前先要设置回调函数setInventoryCallback(IUHFInventoryCallback),然后调用盘点函数RFIDWithUHFUART.startInventoryTag()开始执行盘点。 注意: 在盘点标签的时候rfid模块只能响应RFIDWithUHFUART.stopInventory()函数。
    For parameter setting, after the connection is successful, call the corresponding function to set parameters and read/write operations. Before inventory labels, set the callback function setInventoryCallback(IUHFInventoryCallback), and then call the counting function RFIDWithUHFUART.startInventoryTag() to start inventory. *Note: When counting labels, the RFID module can only respond to the RFIDWithUHFUART.stopInventory() function

    第三步,在已设置的setInventoryCallback(IUHFInventoryCallback)盘点回调接口的callback()函数中处理盘点到的标签数据
    Step 3: Process the inventoried label data in the callback function of the setInventoryCallback(IUHFInventoryCallback) callback interface

    第四步：退出app调用 RFIDWithUHFUART.free()断开连接，如果断开之前正在盘点，请先停止盘点，在断开连接。
    Step 4: Exit the app and call RFIDWithUHFUART.free() to disconnect. If you are taking inventory before disconnecting, please stop the inventory first and then disconnecting.

    Example Usage:
    public class UHFDemo() {
     M775Authenticate rfid = M775Authenticate.getInstance();
     boolean isInventory=false;
     public void uhf(){
      boolean result = rfid.init(context);
      if (!result) {
      //connect fail
      return;
     }
     //connect success
     //configuration parameters
     // rfid.setFrequencyMode(xx);
     // rfid.setPower(30);
     rfid.setInventoryCallback(new M775Authenticate.IUHFInventoryCallback() {
      public void callback(M775Authenticate.AuthenticateInfo authenticateInfo) {
       if (authenticateInfo != null) {
       //Processing tags
       }
      }
     });
     if (rfid.startInventoryTag()) {
     //success
     isInventory=true;
     } else {
     rfid.stopInventory();
     //fail
     }
     //..............
     rfid.stopInventory();
     isInventory=false;
     //.................
     //disconnect uhf

     rfid.free();
      }
